  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CElement, java.util.Iterator

    public class CAndTag
extends CTag
    A CAndTag is a CTag corresponding to the set of shapes tagged by a CTag t1 and a CTag t2.
    Author:
    Caroline Appert
